<p class="head">29<sup>th</sup> October, Continued</p>
<p style="text-align:justify;">much in want of the principal thing to make <span class="AddHand-editors">[t]</span>he in<span class="AddHand-editors">[side]</span> <span class="AddHand-editors">[com]</span>fortable, for my Men who were trying for a fall fish<span class="AddHand-editors">[ing]</span>, returned to Day, and Only got 400 fish in all, so that if <span class="AddHand-editors">[the]</span> Lake is no better in Winter, than now, which is very Seld<span class="AddHand-editors">[om]</span> the Case in any Lake, the Lord have Mercy Upon us, for we Shall be in a Sad Situation, as I Exspect no assistance from the Indians who are all Starving as yet themselve<span class="AddHand-editors">[s.]</span></p>
<p style="text-align:justify;">Some people, who may peruse this, will perhaps <span class="AddHand-editors">[wish]</span> to know what a fall fishing means, and how the fis<span class="AddHand-editors">[h]</span> <span class="AddHand-editors">[are]</span> preserved without Salt<span class="AddHand-editors">[.]</span>  I shall describe both, as well <span class="AddHand-editors">[as]</span> I Can<span class="AddHand-editors">[.]</span>  <span class="AddHand-editors">[I]</span>n the Month of October, the white fish re<span class="AddHand-editors">[turn]</span> from the Deep Water to Spawn on Shaul Banks <span class="Gap">[&#8230;]</span> Sandy, or Gravelly Bottoms, or to a Shaul Entrance <span class="AddHand-editors">[of]</span> a River where there is Some Current, which is s<span class="AddHand-editors">[till]</span> prefareable, as they resort in greater Numbers to the <span class="Gap">[&#8230;]</span> when Such a place Can be found, and here a Verie<span class="AddHand-editors">[ty]</span> of Other fish gathers, to feed on the Roes of the wh<span class="AddHand-editors">[ite]</span> fish, so that in a good Spawning place, they Some <span class="AddHand-editors">[times]</span> get 2 or 300 fish in One Night, Out of <span class="Gap">[&#8230;]</span> which they visit Several times each ni<span class="AddHand-editors">[ght]</span> <span class="Gap">[&#8230;]</span></p>

